<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Book Appointment</title>
    <style>
      @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poppins:400,500,600,700&display=swap");
      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
      }
      html,
      body {
        height: 100%;
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center; /* Aligning horizontally */
        align-items: center; /* Aligning vertically */
        background: -webkit-linear-gradient(
          left,
          rgba(33, 8, 28, 1),
          #4d1434,
          rgba(77, 20, 52, 1)
        );
      }
      .wrapper {
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column; /* Aligning items in a column */
        align-items: center; /* Aligning items to the center horizontally */
        width: 80%; /* Adjusting width to fill the screen */
        height: 60%;
        background: #fff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0px 15px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .business-details {
        width: 100%; /* Adjusting width */
        height: 90%;
        background: #4d1434; /* Adjusting background color */
        border-radius: 15px;
        padding: 40px; /* Adjusting padding */
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 20px; /* Adjusting font size */
        line-height: 1.5; /* Adjusting line height */
      }
      .form-wrapper {
        display: none;
        position: absolute;
        top: 50%;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
        background: #fff;
        padding: 30px;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0px 15px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        z-index: 2;
        width: 40%;
        height: 68%;
      }

      .close-button {
        position: absolute;
        top: 10px;
        left: 10px;
        font-size: 24px;
        cursor: pointer;
        z-index: 2;
      }
      .close-button:hover {
        color: #4d1434;
      }
      .form-inner form {
        width: 100%;
        z-index: 2;
      }
      .form-inner form .field {
        height: 50px;
        width: 100%;
        margin-top: 20px;
        z-index: 2;
      }
      .form-inner form .field input[type="date"],
      .form-inner form .field textarea,
      .form-inner form .field select {
        height: 50px; /* Adjust height */
        width: 100%;
        outline: none;
        padding-left: 15px;
        border-radius: 15px;
        border: 1px solid lightgrey;
        border-bottom-width: 2px;
        font-size: 17px;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        resize: none; /* Disable resizing */
        z-index: 2;
      }
      .form-inner form .field input:focus::placeholder,
      .form-inner form .field select:focus::placeholder {
        color: #4d1434;
      }
      .form-inner form .field select:hover option {
        background-color: transparent;
        color: inherit;
      }
      .form-inner form .field select:hover {
        outline: none;
      }
      .show-form-button {
        background: #4d1434; /* Adjusting button color */
        color: white;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        font-size: 16px;
        cursor: pointer;
        margin-top: 20px;
        z-index: 2;
      }
      /* Add a class to darken the page */
      .darken {
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Darken the background */
        position: fixed;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        z-index: 1; /* Ensure it's above other elements */
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="business-details">
        <!-- Placeholder business details -->
        <h2>Business Details</h2>
        <p>
          Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Fusce et
          vestibulum arcu, at laoreet neque. Proin id commodo odio. Lorem ipsum
          dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Pariatur modi veritatis
          optio distinctio saepe fuga repudiandae iste fugit est ad voluptates
          debitis nemo consequatur quaerat corporis, sapiente architecto natus!
          Nam?
        </p>
      </div>
      <button class="show-form-button" style="z-index: 1" onclick="showForm()">
        Book Appointment
      </button>
      <!-- Add a wrapper for the dark overlay -->
      <div id="darkOverlay" class="darken" style="display: none"></div>
      <div class="form-wrapper" id="form-wrapper">
        <div class="form-inner">
          <span class="close-button" onclick="closeForm()">Ã—</span>
          <form method="post" autocomplete="off" onsubmit="return validation()">
            <div class="field">
              <input name="date" type="date" required />
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <textarea
                name="issue"
                rows="4"
                placeholder="Describe the issue"
                required
              ></textarea>
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <select name="service" required>
                <option value="" disabled selected>Select Service</option>
                <option value="pest_control">Pest Control</option>
                <option value="moving">Moving</option>
                <option value="cleaning">Cleaning</option>
                <option value="repairs">Repairs</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <input type="submit" value="Book Now" class="show-form-button" />
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script>
      function showForm() {
        document.getElementById("form-wrapper").style.display = "block";
        document.getElementById("darkOverlay").style.display = "block"; // Show the dark overlay
      }
      function closeForm() {
        document.getElementById("form-wrapper").style.display = "none";
        document.getElementById("darkOverlay").style.display = "none"; // Hide the dark overlay
      }
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
